## Job Description 7
**Role:** Associate Business Consultant (Product Implementation)
**Industry:** Software Product (ION)

### Responsibilities
* Provide business analysis and troubleshooting in all phases of the project.
* Assume hands-on project implementation duties (initiate, design, build, test, deploy).
* Gather and document business requirements, configuration designs, and test plans.

**Associated Skills:**
* **Client Advisory:** Requirement Understanding, Problem Clarification, Root Cause Identification
* **Project Management:** Work Progress Monitoring, Delivery Follow-Ups
* **Reporting and Documentation:** Status Report Preparation, Insight Summarization, Document Structuring
* **Operations Support:** Execution Assistance, Coordination with Operations Teams

